text.section:
The Board of Regents shall submit to the Governor and, in accordance with § 2-1246 of the State Government Article, the General Assembly, an annual report on:
The business entities established in accordance with this section;
Funds invested in, and financing provided to, business entities established in accordance with this section;
Ownership interests in any business entities established in accordance with this section; and
The current status of the business entities.
